title: The Vampire Diaries
plot: After centuries of quarreling, Stefan and Damon Salvatore return to their original town of Mystic Fall Virginia. Stefan, the selfless, brave, guilt ridden brothers meets a high school girl named Elena Gilbert who he instantly falls in love with. While Damon the gorgeous, dangerous, and selfish vampire is after his brothers girl to pay him back for making him turn into a vampire in 1864.
stars: Nina Dobrev, Paul Wesley, Ian Somerhalder, Kat Graham
genres: Drama, Fantasy, Horror, Mystery, Romance, Thriller
companies: Outerbanks Entertainment, Alloy Entertainment, CBS Television Studios

similars.title: The Originals
similars.plot: A family of power-hungry thousand-year-old vampires look to take back the city that they built and dominate all those who have done them wrong.
similars.stars: Joseph Morgan, Daniel Gillies, Claire Holt

similars.title: Teen Wolf
similars.plot: An average high school student and his best friend get caught up in some trouble causing him to receive a werewolf bite. As a result they find themselves in the middle of all sorts of dramas in Beacon Hills.
similars.stars: Tyler Posey, Holland Roden, Dylan O'Brien

similars.title: Legacies
similars.plot: Hope Mikaelson, a tribrid daughter of a Vampire/Werewolf hybrid, makes her way in the world.
similars.stars: Danielle Rose Russell, Aria Shahghasemi, Kaylee Bryant

similars.title: Gossip Girl
similars.plot: Privileged teens living on the Upper East Side of New York can hide no secret from the ruthless blogger who is always watching.
similars.stars: Blake Lively, Leighton Meester, Penn Badgley

similars.title: The Originals: Awakening
similars.plot: The story of Kol Mikaelson one of the wildest of the original family and how he spent his time in New Orleans.
similars.stars: Nathaniel Buzolic, Keri Lynn Pratt, Aleeah Rogers

similars.title: Pretty Little Liars
similars.plot: Four friends band together against an anonymous foe who threatens to reveal their darkest secrets, while also investigating the disappearance of their best friend.
similars.stars: Troian Bellisario, Ashley Benson, Lucy Hale

similars.title: The Vampire Diaries: A Darker Truth
similars.fullTitle: The Vampire Diaries: A Darker Truth (2009)
similars.plot: Follows the investigation of Jason Harris into the murder of his sister Joanne. He follows Stefan Salvatore from NYC to Mystic Falls, believing him to be a vampire and his sister's killer.
similars.stars: Matt Perello, Molly O'Neill, Kat Slatery

similars.title: Riverdale
similars.plot: While navigating the troubled waters of romance, school and family, Archie and his gang become entangled in dark Riverdale mysteries.

similars.title: Shadowhunters
similars.plot: After her mother disappears, Clary must venture into the dark world of demon hunting, and embrace her new role among the Shadowhunters.
similars.stars: Katherine McNamara, Dominic Sherwood, Alberto Rosende

similars.title: The 100
similars.plot: Set ninety-seven years after a nuclear war has destroyed civilization, when a spaceship housing humanity's lone survivors sends one hundred juvenile delinquents back to Earth, in hopes of possibly re-populating the planet.
similars.stars: Eliza Taylor, Bob Morley, Marie Avgeropoulos

similars.title: Once Upon a Time
similars.plot: A young woman with a troubled past is drawn to a small town in Maine where fairy tales are to be believed.
similars.stars: Ginnifer Goodwin, Jennifer Morrison, Lana Parrilla

similars.title: You
similars.plot: A dangerously charming, intensely obsessive young man goes to extreme measures to insert himself into the lives of those he is transfixed by.
similars.stars: Penn Badgley, Victoria Pedretti, Ambyr Childers
